  "title": "AB03 - Accounts Admin",
  "description": "<p><strong>Accounts Admin</strong></p><ul><li>Working Days: 5 Days</li><li>Working Timing: 9am-6pm</li><li>Opp Marymount Stn</li><li>Salary: $2,200- $2,800 (Depends on Experience)</li></ul><p><u><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></u></p><ul><li><p>Assist senior in administrative support and ad-hoc finance tasks</p></li><li><p>Second to client’s place in providing administrative support independently</p></li><li><p>Handle accounts payable and receivable, including invoicing, payments, and follow-ups</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate financial records and proper filing of accounting documents</p></li><li><p>Perform data entry for transactions into accounting systems</p></li><li><p>Reconcile bank statements and assist with month-end closing</p></li><li><p>Prepare payment advise as requested by client</p></li></ul><p><u><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></u></p><ul><li>Certifications in Accountancy</li><li>1 year of working experience in relevant roles preferred</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
